<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10562274>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. External morphology of Ocnus planci. A. General view (a. ventral side b. dorsal side), B. Posterior part (a. anus with 4 anal teeth indicated by red arrows, b. whole individual), C. Tentacles indicated by red arrows (a. lateral view, b. top view), D. Internal anatomy (a. whole individual, b. buccal part)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10562274/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.10562276>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Ossicles of O. planci. A. Ventral side. B. Dorsal side. C. Introvert. D. Podia. E. Anal region. F. Anterior end. G. Tentacles. H. Calcareous ring (R = radial plates, IR = interradial plates). Scale bar A–G = 50 µm, H = 1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/10562276/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

